#: src/qualcoder/information.py:454
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Manage\n"
"\n"
"The Manage tab displays workspaces for organising cases, files, attributes, journals, and references.\n"
"Use the [Manage menu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases) to choose among them.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Files](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_files)\n"
"\n"
"- This menu lets you add and remove empirical data in your project.\n"
"- You can import plain text and many other document types,\n"
"including PDFs, images, audio, and video.\n"
"- You may also import survey data.\n"
"- Before importing text files, you may want to create pseudonyms to protect the privacy of people or organisations.\n"
"- [Help: Import files](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Files/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Cases](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_cases)\n"
"\n"
"- You can use cases to group files together that are related to a topic, person, organisation, or any other empirical entity in your study. \n"
"- This can be useful for organising your data and for running reports on specific groups of files.\n"
"- [Help: Cases](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Journals](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Journals are used to record your thoughts when coding and analysing data. \n"
"- The journal window opens separately from the main window so you can move between them easily.\n"
"- [Help: Journals](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Attributes](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Files, cases, and journals can have attributes (variables) that describe their characteristics. \n"
"- They can be used to filter and organise data, and to run reports based on specific criteria. \n"
"- Use this menu to create and manage such attributes. They can be attached to files, cases, and journals directly in the respective workspaces. \n"
"- [Help: Attributes](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage References](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_references)\n"
"\n"
"- Bibliographic references can be imported from NBIB and RIS files.\n"
"- After that, references can be linked to files in the project.\n"
"- [Help: Import References](qualcoder://help/6.1.-Imports-and-Exports/)\n"
msgstr ""
"# Kudeatu\n"
"\n"
"Kudeatu fitxak laneko areak erakusten ditu kasu, fitxategi, atributu, aldizkari eta erreferentziak antolatzeko.\n"
"Erabili [Kudeatu menua] (qualcoder://menu/files and cases) haien artean aukeratzeko.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Kudeatu-fitxategiak](qualcoder://menu/files and cases/manage files)\n"
"\n"
"Menu honek zure proiektuan datu enpirikoak gehitu eta kentzeko aukera ematen dizu.\n"
"- Testu soila eta beste dokumentu mota asko inporta ditzakezu.\n"
"PDFak, irudiak, audioa eta bideoa barne.\n"
"- Inkestaren datuak ere inporta ditzakezu.\n"
"- Testu-fitxategiak inportatu aurretik, pseudonimoak sortu nahi dituzu pertsonen edo erakundeen pribatutasuna babesteko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Inportatu fitxategiak](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Fitxategiak/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Manage Cases](qualcoder://menu/files and cases/manage cases)\n"
"\n"
"- Kasuak erabil ditzakezu gai, pertsona, erakunde edo beste edozein erakunde enpirikorekin zerikusia duten fitxategiak elkartzeko.\n"
"- Erabilgarria izan daiteke zure datuak antolatzeko eta fitxategi-talde zehatzei buruzko txostenak egiteko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Kasuak](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Manage Journals](qualcoder://menu/files and cases/manage journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Egunkariak erabiltzen dira zure pentsamenduak grabatzeko datuak kodetzean eta aztertzean.\n"
"- Egunkari-leihoa leiho nagusitik bereizita irekitzen da, erraz mugitzeko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: egunkariak](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Kudeatu atributuak](qualcoder://menu/files and cases/manage attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Fitxategiak, kasuak eta egunkariak beren ezaugarriak azaltzen dituzten atributuak (aldagarriak) izan ditzakete.\n"
"- Datuak iragazteko eta antolatzeko erabil daitezke, eta txostenak egiteko irizpide zehatzen arabera.\n"
"- Erabili menu hau atributu horiek sortzeko eta kudeatzeko. Fitxategi, kasu eta aldizkariei zuzenean erantsi ahal izango zaizkie dagozkien laneko areetan.\n"
"- [Laguntza: atributuak](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Erreferentziak](qualcoder://menu/files and cases/manage references)\n"
"\n"
"- Erreferentzia bibliografikoak NBIB eta RIS fitxategietatik inportatu daitezke.\n"
"- Ondoren, erreferentziak proiektuaren fitxategiekin esteka daitezke.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Inportatu erreferentziak] (qualcoder://help/6.1.- Imports-and-Exports/)"

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:503
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Coding\n"
"\n"
"The Coding tab displays workspaces for coding text, PDFs, images, audio, and video.\n"
"Use the [Coding menu](qualcoder://menu/coding) to select an option to begin. \n"
"Note that you can only open a particular coding workspace if that type of data is actually present in the current project. \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Text](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to read textual data closely and assign codes to selected passages.\n"
"- You can organise codes in a tree, add memos and annotations, create bookmarks, and mark especially useful segments as important.\n"
"- [Help: Coding text](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Images](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_image)\n"
"\n"
"- In this workspace, you can select regions in photographs, diagrams, screenshots, or other visual material and assign codes to them.\n"
"- Coded areas are displayed as coloured rectangles linked to your code system.\n"
"- [Help: Coding images](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Audio and Video](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_audio_video)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to transcribe and/or code time-based media such as interviews, focus groups, and field recordings.\n"
"- [Help: Coding audio and video](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-and-Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code PDFs](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- This workspace allows you to code text directly in PDF documents when you want to keep the original page layout in view.\n"
"- This is useful for articles, reports, and other source material where page position and formatting matter.\n"
"- [Help: Coding PDFs](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Assisted Coding](qualcoder://menu/coding/ai_assisted_coding)\n"
"\n"
"- This loads a variant of the text coding workspace that uses AI to explore your data and suggest segments for a selected code.\n"
"- [Help: AI assisted coding](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Organiser](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to reorganise your code system using a graphical, mind-map style interface.\n"
"- You can move, merge, and rename codes and categories as your analytic structure becomes clearer.\n"
"- [Help: Code Organiser](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Colour Scheme](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour_scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- This allows you to change the colour scheme of your codes and categories. \n"
"- Special schemes for colour-blind users are available. \n"
msgstr ""
"♪ Coding\n"
"\n"
"Coding fitxak testuak, PDFak, irudiak, audioa eta bideoa kodetzeko laneko areak bistaratzen ditu.\n"
"Erabili menu nagusia (qualcoder://menu/coding) hasteko aukera hautatzeko.\n"
"Kontuan izan kodetze-espazio jakin bat bakarrik ireki dezakezula datu mota hori uneko proiektuan badago.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Testu kodea](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili laneko area hau testu-datuak arretaz irakurtzeko eta hautatutako pasarteei kodeak esleitzeko.\n"
"- Zuhaitz batean kodeak antola ditzakezu, zirkularrak eta oharrak gehitu, laster-markak sortu eta segmentu oso erabilgarriak markatu.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Coding text](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Kode-irudiak](qualcoder://menu/coding/code image)\n"
"\n"
"Laneko area honetan, eskualdeak hauta ditzakezu argazkietan, diagrametan, pantaila-argazkian edo beste material bisual batean, eta kodeak esleitu.\n"
"-Kodeatutako eremuak zure kode-sistemari lotutako laukizuzen koloreztatu gisa bistaratzen dira.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Coding images](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Audioa eta bideoa](qualcoder://menu/coding/code audio video)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili laneko area hau denbora-mugan oinarritutako multimediak transkribatzeko eta/edo kodetzeko, hala nola elkarrizketak, foku-taldeak eta eremu-grabazioak.\n"
"- [Laguntza: audioa eta bideoa](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-and-Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [PDF kodea](qualcoder://menu/coding/code pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- Laneko area honek testua zuzenean PDF dokumentuetan kodetzeko aukera ematen dizu jatorrizko orrialdearen diseinua ikusteko.\n"
"- Artikulu, txosten eta iturburuko beste materialetarako erabilgarria da, non orrialdearen posizioa eta formatua ematen duen.\n"
"- [Help: Coding PDFs](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [AI Assisted Coding](qualcoder://menu/coding/ai assisted coding)\n"
"\n"
"- Testu-kodeketako laneko arearen aldaera bat kargatzen du, AA erabiltzen duena zure datuak aztertzeko eta hautatutako kode baterako segmentuak proposatzeko.\n"
"- [Laguntza: AAk lagundutako kodeketa](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Kode Antolatzailea](qualcoder://menu/coding/code organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Erabili laneko area hau zure kode-sistema berrantolatzeko, estilo grafikoko interfazea erabiliz.\n"
"-Kodeak eta kategoriak mugi, batu eta alda ditzakezu, zure egitura analitikoa argiagotu ahala.\n"
"- [Laguntza: Kode Antolatzailea](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Colour Scheme](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- Zure kodeen eta kategorien kolore-eskema alda dezakezu.\n"
"- Kolore itsuen erabiltzaileentzako eskema bereziak daude erabilgarri."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:560
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Reports tab\n"
"\n"
"This tab displays tools from both the [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis) and [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports) menus.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want to explore coded segments and relationships in detail.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Retrieval and segment-based analysis\n"
"\n"
"These tools help you inspect the actual coded material in your project.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code retrieval](qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding_reports) is a flexible analysis tool. It gathers all segments for selected codes or categories and lets you narrow the results by file, case, attributes, or search text.\n"
"- [Codes by text segments](qualcoder://menu/analysis/text_segments_by_codes) generates a table with text segments and all associated codes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Code relationships and overlaps\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools to examine how codes relate to one another. They only work with text files.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code relations](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_relations) shows proximity, overlap, inclusion, and exact matches between selected codes.\n"
"- [Code co-occurrence](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_co_occurrence) focuses on where two codes overlap or directly touch.\n"
"- [Code text exact matches](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_text_exact_matches) lists passages where different codes were applied to exactly the same text.\n"
"- [Graph](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view_graph) provides a visual, mind-map style view of linked project elements like codes, cases, files, etc. [Help: Graph](qualcoder://help/5.4.-Graph/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want summaries, comparisons, counts, charts, or exports for reporting purposes.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Inter-Coder Comparisons\n"
"\n"
"- [Coding comparison](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison) and [Coding comparison by file](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison_by_file) are especially useful for collaborative work and inter-coder checking.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Summaries, frequencies, and charts\n"
"\n"
"These reports summarise patterns across the project rather than showing every coded segment in detail.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code frequencies](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_frequencies) counts how often codes and categories have been used.\n"
"- [Code counts by file/case](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_comparison_table) gives a compact overview of where selected codes appear most often.\n"
"- [File summary](qualcoder://menu/reports/file_summary) and [Code summary](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_summary) give focused overviews of one file or one code at a time.\n"
"- [Charts](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) visualises distributions and comparisons with diagrams such as bar charts, treemaps, and heatmaps.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Advanced reporting\n"
"\n"
"- [Database queries](qualcoder://menu/reports/sql_statements) gives direct access to the project database for custom analyses. This is most useful when the standard reports do not answer a specific research question in the exact form you need.\n"
msgstr ""
"# Txostenak fitxa\n"
"\n"
"Fitxa honek tresnak erakusten ditu bi menuetatik:qualcoder://menu/analysis) eta [Reports] (qualcoder://menu/reports).\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek kodetutako segmentuak eta harremanak xehetasunez aztertu nahi dituzunean.\n"
"\n"
"[Laguntza: analisi eta txostenen menu-aukerak](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"- Berreskuratzea eta segmentuan oinarritutako analisia\n"
"\n"
"Tresna hauek zure proiektuan kodetutako materiala ikuskatzen laguntzen dizute.\n"
"\n"
"-(qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding reports) analisi-tresna malgua da. Hautatutako kode edo kategorien segmentu guztiak biltzen ditu, eta emaitzak fitxategi, kasu, atributu edo bilaketa-testuaren bidez murrizten uzten dizu.\n"
"- [Testu-segmentuen arabera kodea] (qualcoder://menu/analysis/text segments by codes) taula bat sortzen du testu-segmentuekin eta lotutako kode guztiekin.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Kode-harremanak eta gainjarriak\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek kodeak elkarren artean nola erlazionatzen diren aztertzeko. Testu-fitxategiekin bakarrik egiten dute lan.\n"
"\n"
"- [Kode-erlazioak] (qualcoder://menu/analysis/code relations) Hurbiltasuna, gainjartzea, inklusioa eta bat datozen zehatzak erakusten ditu hautatutako kodeen artean.\n"
"- [Kode co-occurrence](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code co occurrence) bi kode gainjartzen edo zuzenean ukitzen diren lekuan zentratzen da.\n"
"- [Kodearen testu zehatza bat dator] (qualcoder://menu/analysis/code text exact matches) pasarteak zerrendatzen ditu, non kode desberdinak testu berari aplikatzen zaizkion.\n"
"- [Graph](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view graph) estekatutako proiektu-elementuen ikuspegi bisuala eskaintzen du, adibidez, kode, kasu, fitxategi eta abar.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [Txostenak](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Erabili tresna hauek laburpenak, konparazioak, zenbaketak, diagramak edo esportazioak nahi dituzunean berri emateko.\n"
"\n"
"[Laguntza: analisi eta txostenen menu-aukerak](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Inter-Coder Comparisons\n"
"\n"
"- [Konparazioa](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding comparison) eta [Coding comparison by file](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding comparison by file) oso erabilgarriak dira lankidetza-lanetarako eta kode-en arteko egiaztaketetarako.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Zenbakiak, maiztasunak eta diagramak\n"
"\n"
"Txosten hauek proiektuaren zehar ereduak laburtzen dituzte, kodetutako segmentu guztiak zehatz-mehatz erakutsi ordez.\n"
"\n"
"- [Kode maiztasuna] (qualcoder://menu/reports/code frequencies) zenbat aldiz erabili diren kodeak eta kategoriak.\n"
"- [Kodea fitxategi/kaxaren arabera kontatzen da] (qualcoder://menu/reports/code comparison table), hautatutako kodeak gehienetan agertzen diren ikuspegi trinkoa ematen du.\n"
"- [Fitxategiaren laburpena](qualcoder://menu/reports/file summary) eta [Kodearen laburpena](qualcoder://menu/reports/code summary) fitxategi baten edo kode baten ikuspegi orokorrak ematen dituzte aldi berean.\n"
"- [Charts](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) diagramen banaketak eta konparazioak erakusten ditu, hala nola barra-diagramak, zuhaitz-mapak eta bero-mapak.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Informazio aurreratua\n"
"\n"
"- [Database kontsultak] (qualcoder://menu/reports/sql statements) proiektuaren datu-basera sarbide zuzena ematen du analisi pertsonalizatuak egiteko. Hau oso erabilgarria da txosten estandarrek ez badute erantzuten ikerketa-gai zehatz bati behar duzun moduan."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:621
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# AI Agent\n"
"\n"
"Here, you can interact with the [AI Agent](qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-based-analysis/) to\n"
"explore your empirical text data, get suggestions for coding, obtain feedback on your codes or memos,\n"
"and generate summaries and reports. To begin, use the [\"New\" button](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new) at \n"
"the bottom left and choose one of the options described below.\n"
"\n"
"{{AI_WARNING_BLOCK}}\n"
"\n"
"## [Chat with the AI Agent](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_general_chat)\n"
"\n"
"- This is the default starting point for an open-ended analysis or any other task.\n"
"- You can also ask for help using QualCoder.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Topic Exploration](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_topic_exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Search and explore a topic or question across the whole corpus of project data.\n"
"- This option opens a dialog where you define the topic and select which data to include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Text Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_text_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Analyse a selected text passage from your empirical material in detail.\n"
"- This will switch to the text coding workspace and let you select a passage for analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Code Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_code_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Discuss your codings with the AI Agent, compare different codes, generate subcodes, or create reports.\n"
"- This will also open a dialog to select the code(s) and data you want to include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Other Options\n"
"- The [AI permissions](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/permissions) control at the bottom left lets you choose what \n"
"the AI Agent is allowed to do in your project.\n"
"- Open the [AI menu](qualcoder://menu/ai) for more options, for example to edit predefined prompts in the\n"
"[prompt library](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_prompts), or start [AI assisted coding](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_search_and_coding).\n"
msgstr ""
"# AI agentea\n"
"\n"
"Hemen, [AI Agent]-ekin elkarreragin dezakezu (qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-analysis/)\n"
"Aztertu testu enpirikoko datuak, kodetzeko iradokizunak lortu, zure kode edo zirkularren oharrak lortu,\n"
"eta laburpenak eta txostenak sortu. Hasteko, erabili [\"Berria\" botoia](qualcoder://ai agent tab/new) at\n"
"behean ezkerrean eta behean azaldutako aukeretako bat aukeratu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"the [Chat with AI Agent](qualcoder://ai agent tab/new/new general chat)\n"
"\n"
"-Abiadura-puntu lehenetsia da azterketa ireki baterako edo beste edozein zereginetarako.\n"
"- Laguntza eska dezakezu QualCoder erabiliz.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [AI Topic Exploration](qualcoder://ai agent tab/new topic exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Bilatu eta aztertu gai edo galdera bat proiektuaren datuen corpus osoan zehar.\n"
"- Aukera honek elkarrizketa-koadro bat irekitzen du gaia definitzeko eta analisian zein datu sartu behar diren hautatzeko.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [AI Text Analysis](qualcoder://ai agent tab/new/new text analysis)\n"
"\n"
"-Zure material enpirikotik hautatutako testu-pasabide bat aztertu.\n"
"- Testu-kodeketako laneko areara aldatuko da eta analisirako pasarte bat hautatuko duzu.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
") [AI kodearen analisia](qualcoder://ai agent tab/new/new code analysis)\n"
"\n"
"-Hitz egin AAko agentearekin kode ezberdinak konparatuz, azpikodeak sortu edo txostenak sortu.\n"
"- Elkarrizketa-koadro bat irekiko da, kodea eta datuak aztertzeko.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
